website_summaries.verdict: Easily the best newt and salamander-specific food available for its top-tier ingredients, healthy balance of vitamins, and easily digested recipe, but its affordability is the cherry on top.
pros: Salmon, halibut, wheat flour, rice bran, and shrimp are the first 5 ingredients
Quick-sinking pellets formulated for aquatic newts and salamanders
cons: These fast-sinking newt and salamander pellets are on the small side, which may not be as appealing for extra-large species

product_meta.title: OMEGA 63111 1 One Newt & Salamander Pellet 1.2oz, Yellow
product_meta.description: Fresh, sustainable seafood - only fresh marine proteins such as wild salmon and Halibut are used in our newt & salamander pellets - No meals, hydrolysates, or protein digests.The result is a superior diet rich in natural color enhancers and OMEGA 3 & 6 fatty acids.
feature_bullets: High lipid, low fiber- these pellets contain an abundance of fresh, natural fats critical for amphibian growth and energy. With fewer starches and carbohydrates, they also provide the ideal low-fiber diet and promote proper digestion.
Essential vitamins & minerals - formulated with the ideal levels of vitamin a, D3, and calcium - All critical for healthy development and the prevention of disease in amphibians.
Less starch; less waste. Low ash for cleaner water
Included Features: Aquarium Natural Meal Free Low Ash Fresh
Age Range Description: All Life Stages
